{
  "stem": "17625.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- she had her hands full.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I looked for a way-- where to stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my cousin, at that time, was-- was-- was a-- a-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] They-- they-- they-- they assembled the people to send them away, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Action.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Action, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Action.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] in German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- they-- they took his parents, my cousin's.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- a-- a few single-- single ones-- me and the cousin and another few boys-- they assigned us a room-- a room in an apartment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was a-- like three rooms, one after the other, going in from one room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And each one-- and we had the last room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was five people, five boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Couldn't get in and out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, you can't-- you find a way to come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but this was after the [NON-ENGLISH], after the-- after the action, there-- there was-- there was no Cracow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was only a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, we stood there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived there for a short time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Gestapo came and looking around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked for-- for-- for-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Partisans, whatever-- illegals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they knocked on the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we put our lock from the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it's means nobody's there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], a-- a-- a gestapo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He kicked the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it opened up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we all spread in the room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One jumped the window.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He broke a hand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took us-- the rest of us, they took us and lined us up downstairs and took us to the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jewish police, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's-- that's what they call it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
